{
  "stem": "11274.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The little girls, the young girls didn't go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I didn't, only on holidays, on New Years, on Rosh Hashanah and, and Yom Kippur for a little while only.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then on, on the Sabbat you would go over after the parents came home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We would go over and bring the cholent home, and we had lunch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in the morning we had-- for, for coffee to warm up, which my mother prepared the day before-- we had a, a Gentile woman coming in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she would light the fire, and it was heating the coffee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And during the war, we weren't allowed to have Gentile help, so we didn't have anything warm on Saturday morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The most of them-- or all of them as far as I know-- refused to, to light the fire themselves.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they rather went without.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For fun, we played dominoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the evening we played cards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- on some-- the holidays and Purim, [? whatever ?] it was, we had a dreidel that we played for, for games to win.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You win if it's a Shin or, or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if you're familiar with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And reading, lots of reading.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was the school library, and there was my lay teacher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I said, one of them was a nun teaching, and one of them in the public school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one of them was a, a, a nun and one lay teacher.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the lay teacher, Mrs.-- Miss [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Bohinska ?] was her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She had a private library herself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so I, I was allowed-- some students were-- and I was, I was sort of a little bit helper of the teacher.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I helped to carry the books home.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
